# jQuery.hideNavbarOnScroll.js

Hide Navbar on Scroll plugin for jQuery 1.11.1 and Bootstrap 3.2.0

# Syntax

```

$('.navbar').hideNavbarOnScroll()

```

# Options

```

$('.navbar').hideNavbarOnScroll({
	'deltaBeforeHide' : 5,
	'hideSpeed'       : 0.4,
});

```

